reviewText:
Pimpinela duet is actually a brother and sister that have been singing together all their lives.  Mis Favoritas DVD and CD, is a phenomenally entertaining work of which I just do not tire of viewing and listen to over and over again.  I am proud to be their loyal fan, so if you like Latin Pop this will not disappoint!

Matanzera56

I really enjoyed growing up with this music, and this cd/dvd combination is a great compilation of their best works. I do highly recommend it to anyone who is a fan.

Me encanto creciendo con esta musica, y esta combinacion de cd/dvd es una exelente compilacion de sus mejores canciones. Se lo recomiendo bastante a cualquier persona que es fanatica.
